commentText: Creates a {@link MongoClient} using the given {@code options}. If the environment_contains a {@code local.mongo.port} property, it is used to configure a client to_an embedded MongoDB instance._@param options the options_@return the Mongo client
codeText: public MongoClient createMongoClient(MongoClientOptions options) {_		Integer embeddedPort = getEmbeddedPort()__		if (embeddedPort != null) {_			return createEmbeddedMongoClient(options, embeddedPort)__		}_		return createNetworkMongoClient(options)__	}
